Description: Estonian ID card management desktop utility
 ID-card Utility is a part of Estonian national ID-card software developed by
 Sertifitseerimiskeskus on behalf of governmental institution - Estonian
 Information Systemâ€™s Authority.
 .
 ID-card utility allows you check the ID-card operation and the validity of the
 certificates, change as well as unblock locked PIN codes and change the PUK
 code. In addition, the utility enables you to renew the certificates, create
 and configure @eesti.ee email address.

